      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "A rousing meeting of the Equal\nSuffrage league is planned for to-\nmorrow evening in the assembly\nroom of the chamber of commerce.\nThe meeting will convene at o\no'clock, and the speakers will be\nMrs. p. P. Stafford and Attorney\nd. B. He'll. There will be a piano\nsolo by Miss Viola krantz and a\nvocal solo by Mrs. George Lovejoy.\n\n\nThe Spokane Press, delivered, 20\ncents a month."
    }
